        "title": "feat(webui): add session workspace rail",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Replace the old right-rail agent file list with a session-scoped workspace rail showing changed files, read files, artifacts, and project browser entries.\n- Add `sessions.files.list` / `sessions.files.get` Gateway RPCs and protocol schemas so the UI can load session-touched files and safe previews.\n- Keep the rail collapsible, keep file previews inside the chat workbench, and preserve split-pane resizing without letting the preview/sidebar overlap the composer.\n- Harden session file reads with workspace-root resolution, `fs-safe` bounded reads, symlink-parent rejection, search traversal limits, integer timestamps, and support for existing transcript tool-call spellings.\n\n## Before / After\n\n### Before\n\nOld rail only exposed a generic agent workspace file list and did not provide session-scoped changed/read/artifact/project context.\n\n![Before session rail](https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/download/session-workspace-rail-proof/before-session-rail.gif)\n\n### After\n\nNew drawer is session-scoped, collapsible, supports file/artifact previews, project browsing, and stays contained beside chat.\n\n![After session workspace rail](https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/download/session-workspace-rail-proof/after-session-workspace-rail.gif)\n\nProof assets are hosted on the fork release: https://github.com/Solvely-Colin/openclaw/releases/tag/session-workspace-rail-proof\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm test src/gateway/server-methods/sessions-files.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `pnpm test ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts ui/src/ui/chat/sidebar-session-picker.browser.test.ts -- --reporter=verbose`\n- `pnpm build`\n- `git diff --check 8f62ec6177aadde8e33fc8ea197c3471e697f1c7`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main --engine codex`\n  - Result: `autoreview clean: no accepted/actionable findings reported`.\n  - Ignored out-of-scope item was verified against the diff: `packages/agent-core/src/agent-loop.ts` is not changed by this branch.\n",
